  Pfizer Inc . did not inform the U.K.
government for more than three months after receiving it that it
had been given a strong internal recommendation to shut its
Sandwich, U.K., research-and-development center, the Financial
Times reported, citing company executives, including Primary
Care Business Unit President Oliver Brandicourt, appearing
before lawmakers on the Science and Technology Committee.  To contact the reporter on this story:
